jAQBe_iGllrr3-hpOcM1tpr4wCKpXwqxN0hUgpo38y8l4i0rS1uS5njyOIslDj9bonyo0w74DtNty5zn9Z5THJX5EEXee1cnpfD_TtotLRvTcYjVqUzuGwtpVoQMOlqBw5EHjT6WnNQOiAYC8TsvXMMQ3CAxoF4fwDZDjcE:1w51Ne:1oVaYyvtqKDlOiwvWdPCKNiyP_JLEAqaqyqe108pd3Q", "expire_date": "2026-04-07T13:01:10.290Z"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.profile", "pk": 1, "fields": {"user": 1, "name": "Anvesh Pandey", "bio": "A technology-focused Computer Science student with strong foundations in programming and data-driven problem solving. Building software and analytical solutions that drive innovation and performance.", "about_bio": "I'm Anvesh Pandey, a Computer Science student focused on developing structured and impactful technology solutions. I combine strong programming fundamentals with data-driven methodologies to address real-world challenges.\r\n\r\nWith a solid foundation in algorithms and data structures, I apply analytical thinking to build efficient and scalable applications. My exposure to data science principles enables me to work with data strategically, extracting insights that support intelligent decision-making.\r\n\r\nMy interests extend to full-stack and backend development, where I work on building structured, maintainable systems designed for long-term efficiency and growth.", "profile_image": "profile_images/my_photo.jpg", "skills": "", "github_url": "https://github.com/anvesh9621", "linkedin_url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anvesh-pandey-7bb094298/", "email_contact": "pandeyanvesh488@gmail.com", "role": "Aspiring Software Developer, Full Stack Developer", "resume": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gCBBTeLeJNjns-kg29taO_gvFTIW3x-v/view?usp=drive_link"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 1, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Bachelor of Technology - Computer Science & Engineering", "institution_name": "Lovely Professional University", "start_date": "2023-08-23", "end_date": null, "is_current": true, "location": "Phagwara, Punjab"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 2, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Intermediate", "institution_name": "Maharishi Vidya Mandir", "start_date": "2021-04-21", "end_date": "2023-03-21", "is_current": false, "location": "Fatehpur, UP"}}, {"model": "accounts_app.education", "pk": 3, "fields": {"profile": 1, "course": "Matriculation", "institution_name": "Maharishi Vidya Mandir", "start_date": "2019-04-21", "end_date": "2021-03-21", "is_current": false, "location": "Fatehpur, UP"}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "Stock Market Prediction & Analytics App", "slug": "stock-market-prediction-analytics-app", "summary": "Machine Learning based Stock Market Prediction and Decision Support System", "description": "Built an AI-powered stock prediction system that forecasts next-day returns and market direction using machine learning models trained on NIFTY-50 historical data.\r\nApplied advanced feature engineering and modeling techniques, including technical indicators (SMA, EMA, RSI, volatility, Bollinger Bands) with Random Forest (regression) and Logistic Regression (classification) for accurate predictions.\r\nDeveloped an interactive Streamlit dashboard to display predictions, confidence levels, Buy/Sell signals, market sentiment, and model insights, enabling data-driven investment decisions.", "tech_stack": "Supervised Learning, Unsupervised Learning, NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib, Streamlit", "github_link": "https://github.com/anvesh9621/stock-market-prediction-app", "live_demo_link": null, "image": "projects/Screenshot_23.png", "featured": false, "created_date": "2026-03-24T14:10:32.993Z"}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Financial Market Risk & Performance Analytics Dashboard", "slug": "fghjgghjk", "summary": "An interactive Power BI dashboard to analyze financial market risk and performance", "description": "Developed an interactive Financial Market Risk & Performance Analytics Dashboard using Power BI to analyze stock and sector performance.\r\nIt provides key insights through metrics like return, volatility, drawdown, and risk-return ratio.\r\nUsers can dynamically filter data by sector, stock, and date range for customized analysis.\r\nThe dashboard includes visualizations such as portfolio trends, risk vs return comparison, and top gainers/losers.\r\nIt helps in making data-driven investment decisions by transforming complex financial data into clear insights.", "tech_stack": "Power BI", "github_link": "https://github.com/anvesh9621/Financial-Market-Risk-Performance-Analytics-Dashboard", "live_demo_link": null, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2025-12-22_135031_h93i3pF.png", "featured": false, "created_date": "2026-03-24T17:23:43.424Z"}}, {"model": "projects_app.project", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "Mediclinic System", "slug": "mediclinic-system", "summary": "Built a multi-clinic SaaS healthcare platform with role-based workflows, appointment management, and event-driven notification system.", "description": "Developed a multi-tenant healthcare system enabling clinics to manage doctors, receptionists, patients, appointments, medical records, and prescriptions with strict RBAC.\r\nImplemented a workflow-driven appointment engine with conflict prevention, status lifecycle management, and audit logging for full traceability.\r\nDesigned an event-driven notification system to trigger real-time and scheduled alerts (booking, confirmation, reminders) using scalable background processing.", "tech_stack": "Django, Django REST Framework, Next.js, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, PostgreSQL, JWT", "github_link": "https://github.com/anvesh9621/Multi-Clinic-Healthcare-Platform", "live_demo_link": null, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2026-03-24_235824.png", "featured": false, "created_date": "2026-03-24T18:34:55.756Z"}}, {"model": "skills_app.skillcategory", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Programming Languages", "slug": "programming-languages", "order": 1, "created_at": "2026-03-24T13:01:47.138Z"}}, {"model": "skills_app.skillcat